commit.title: Giving a name to "print" functions in Names which tells it is for debugging.
commit.message:
Giving a name to "print" functions in Names which tells it is for debugging.

The "print" and "to_string" functions in Names were printing full
names (not taking into account visibility). They were also printing
"#" for sections, which is not part of the user-level syntax of names.

We requalify them as "debug" printers.
